quran[22]{c,v,t}:
  54,1,“Nthawi ya chimaliziro (Qiyâma) yayandikira ndipo mwezi wagawikana
  54,2,"“Koma akaona chozizwitsa akunyoza ndi kunena kuti: “Awa ndi matsenga womkeramkera patsogolo.”"
  54,3,“Ndipo adatsutsa (choonadi) ndi kutsatira zilakolako (zawo zoipa) koma chinthu chilichonse (cha Allah) nchokhazikika
  54,4,“Ndipo ndithu zidawafika nkhani zomwe zili zokwanira kuwaopseza
  54,5,“Nzeru zokwana koma machenjezo (kwa iwo) sanawathandize
  54,6,"“Choncho, apewe (iwe Mtumiki) osakhulupirira, (yembekezani) tsiku loitana woitana (wa Allah) ku chinthu chovuta kwambiri, (chodedwa ndi mitima)"
  54,7,“Maso awo ali zyoli chifukwa chakuopsa; adzatuluka m’manda uku ali ngati dzombe lobalalika (chifukwa cha kuchuluka)
  54,8,"“Akuthamangira kwa woitana (uku atatukula mitu yawo, osatha kucheukira kwina). Adzanena osakhulupirira (tsiku lachiweruziro): “Ili nditsiku lovuta kwambiri.”"
  54,9,"“Patsogolo pawo (Aquraishi) anthu a Nuh nawo adatsutsa, adamtsutsa kapolo Wathu nanena kuti: “Uyu ngwamisala!” Ndipo adaopsezedwa (ndi kuzunzidwa ndi mazunzo osiyanasiyana)"
  54,10,"“(Nuh) adaitana Mbuye wake (nati): “Ine ndagonjetsedwa (ndi anthu anga); choncho ndipulumutseni (kwa iwo).”"
  54,11,"“Tero tidatsekula makomo akumwamba ndi madzi otsika mopitiriza, mwamphamvu"
  54,12,“Ndipo tidaing’amba nthaka kukhala ndi akasupe (ofwamphuka madzi mwamphamvu). Choncho adakumana madzi (akumwamba ndi am’nthaka kuti awaononge) pamuyeso wopimidwa ndi kulamulidwa (ndi Allah)
  54,13,“Ndipo tidamnyamula Nuh pa chombo chamatabwa chokhomedwa ndi misomali (yamitengo)
  54,14,“Chinkayandama pamadzi ndi kuyang’aniridwa ndi Ife. Iyi ndi mphoto ya (Nuh) yemwe adakanidwa ndi anthu ake
  54,15,“Ndipo ndithu tidachisiya (chigumula) kukhala phunziro (pakuonongeka kwa osakhulupirira ndi kupulumuka kwa okhulupirira). Kodi alipo wolikumbukira (ndi kupeza nalo malango abwino)
  54,16,“Kodi chidali bwanji chilango Changa ndi machenjezo Anga (kwa onyoza)
  54,17,“Ndipo ndithu taifewetsa Qur’an kuti ikhale chikumbutso. Kodi alipo woikumbukira (ndi kupeza nayo malangizo abwino)
  54,18,"“Âdi adamtsutsa (mneneri wawo Hud), kodi chidali bwanji chilango Changa ndi machenjezo Anga (kwa onyoza)"
  54,19,"“Ndithu Ife tidawatumizira mphepo yozizira, yaphokoso, m’tsiku latsoka lopitilira"
  54,20,“Idawazula anthu (kuchoka m’malo mwawo ndi kuwaponya panthaka ali akufa) ngati matsinde a mitengo yakanjedza ozulidwa m’malo mwake
  54,21,“Kodi chidali bwanji chilango Changa ndi machenjezo Anga (kwa onyoza)
  54,22,“Ndipo ndithu taifewetsa Qur’an kuti ikhale chikumbutso. Kodi alipo woikumbukira (ndi kupeza nayo malangizo abwino)